		  ({Q}o{S}) guarantees. {M}oreover, finding the multicast
		  structure with respect to the defined {Q}o{S} requirements
		  while minimizing a cost function is an {NP}-difficult
		  optimization problem. {A}ccording to the state-of-the-art,
		  to solve the multi-constrained multicast routing problem,
